com.siemens.ct.exi.attributes
Interface AttributeList

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractAttributeList, AttributeListSchemaInformed, AttributeListSchemaLess
public interface AttributeList

Namespace (NS) and attribute (AT) events are encoded in a specific order following the associated start element (SE) event. Namespace (NS) events are encoded first, in document order, followed by the AT(xsi:type) event if present, followed by the rest of the attribute (AT) events. When schemas are used, attribute events occur in lexical order sorted first by qname localName then by qname uri.

Version:
0.7
Author:
